data.description: **15k PRICE IMPROVEMENT** Welcome to your next home with an option for a ASSUMABLE VA loan with a 2.25% interest rate! Immerse yourself in the best of Colorado living in this stunning ranch-style home that offers the perfect blend of modern and small-town charm! As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the spacious and inviting living area with plantation shutters throughout the home - that's perfect for hosting friends and family. The primary suite offers a true retreat with a private ensuite bath; all on the main level! Need more space? You're in luck! This gem boasts a fully finished basement, ready to be transformed into the ultimate entertainment zone, or that personal gym you've always dreamed of. Nestled on a prime corner lot, this home enjoys an abundance of natural light that's truly unparalleled. This large lot is beautifully landscaped, surrounded with trees, and is perfect for summertime barbecues and outdoor fun. What's even more exciting? Right across the street, you'll discover a community park that's perfect for picnics, playtime, and leisurely strolls. For those with children, you'll appreciate the convenience of having schools within walking distance. Outdoor enthusiasts, you're in for a treat! The Johnstown Reservoir is a short distance away. Enjoy fishing, and picturesque sunsets whenever you desire. New developments include a fantastic Ledge Rock shopping center, a new golf course and the ever-popular Buc-ee's, where you can explore a variety of restaurants right at your fingertips. You're just a short drive from I-25, making your daily journey a breeze. This exceptional home has it all! From the incredible primary suite to the community perks, it's a golden opportunity for a lifestyle upgrade. Don't wait -Your new chapter begins here!
